{"type": "article", "id": 12110, "title": "便携式打印机", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-15T11:03:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151414UVDgxCHs3nM0WK7k.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t Droprinter 是一个便携式的智能打印机，和智能手机，可以在出差或户外方便使用，它能够打印文本，照片，网站页面等一切出现在手机屏幕上的东西，使用的是热敏感纸，平均每张打印仅需花费 2 美分，同时，避免了携带油墨的尴尬。目前产品正在众筹。<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/droprinter/droprinter-the-worlds-first-smart-phone-printer\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以支持他们。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135958QIqECNnLthFvjP3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135959N8XAyamKQI5o0O7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140000TX9siI7kqOVhRQxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70735294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140000th1GfcysuaoSHglk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}